 trial at Scone would have tightened up his condition. He draws well and won't be in this class for much longer. 10. RAYGUN ROCKS has changed stables since last racing and is resuming from a long spell without the aid of any public trials. She is in good hands, and the market will be an important guide to her chances. 1. HANUMAN resumed from a spell for a new trainer and was made favourite. He peaked on his run that day, which was his first in NSW after previously racing in Victoria, and he would have taken a lot of benefit from that hit-out. The small field will suit him, and he can set the record straight in this, so follow your money. 3. CORKY makes his debut, and he was not too far away in a recent trial over 900m. Include in all combinations.\",\"runners\":[5,10,1,3],\"exclusive\":true}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Dan Missen","tipRunnerNumbers":[5,1,8,2]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[10,5,1,2]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[10,1,5,2]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,5,3,6]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,5,2,10]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,1,2,3]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,3,8,6]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,5,2,10]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":1,"venueMnemonic":"WTN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":1,"venueMnemonic":"WTN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":1,"venueMnemonic":"WTN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":1,"venueMnemonic":"WTN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":1,"venueMnemonic":"WTN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":1,"venueMnemonic":"WTN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":1,"venueMnemonic":"WTN","raceType":"R"}},{"w